      "name": "Tobacco - Age of Initiation of Use - Adolescent",
      "code": "PX030701",
      "abbreviation": "PX030701",
      "description": "Measurement to ascertain the respondent’s age of initiation of first/regular use of cigarettes, which can be used to calculate duration of use and pack-years measures.",
